### Step 2 — Paste this in root `.gitignore`
```
# Dependencies
node_modules/
client/node_modules/
server/node_modules/

# Environment files — NEVER commit these!
.env
server/.env
# client/.env
*.env

# Build files
client/dist/
client/build/

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/